---
/*
  Steps — "How it works" in 3 plain steps. One idea: getting started
  is simple and low-risk.
*/
---
<section id="how" class="section" aria-labelledby="how-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">How it works</div>
      <h2 id="how-heading" class="section-h2">
        Up and running in three<br>
        <span class="text-amber">simple, no-pressure steps.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <ol class="steps-grid" role="list">
      <li class="step reveal">
        <span class="step-num">01</span>
        <h3>Tell us about your business</h3>
        <p>A quick chat or quote form. We learn what you do and recommend the simplest setup that fits, with no jargon and no pressure.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="step reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <span class="step-num">02</span>
        <h3>We build and secure it</h3>
        <p>Website, domain, hosting, business email, SEO and security, all built fast and done properly, ready to launch.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="step reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <span class="step-num">03</span>
        <h3>We manage it every month</h3>
        <p>Hosting, checks, updates, content and your AI receptionist, handled monthly so your site stays fast, secure and visible.</p>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <div class="steps-cta reveal">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-amber btn-lg">Get a Quote</a>
      <a href="/how-it-works" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">See the full process</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #how { padding-block: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem); }
  #how .section-head { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.75rem); text-align: center; }
  #how .eyebrow { justify-content: center; }

  .steps-grid {
    list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(1rem, 2.4vw, 2rem);
    counter-reset: step;
  }
  .step { position: relative; padding-top: 1.5rem; }
  .step::before {
    content: ""; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--amber), transparent);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .step-num {
    display: block; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .9rem;
    letter-spacing: .1em; color: var(--amber-300); margin-bottom: .9rem;
  }
  .step h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 1.4vw, 1.35rem); line-height: 1.25; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #fff; margin: 0 0 .55rem;
  }
  .step p { margin: 0; font-size: .96rem; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,.66); max-width: 34ch; }

  .steps-cta {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: .75rem;
    margin-top: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
  }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 520px; margin-inline: auto; gap: 1.75rem; }
    .step p { max-width: none; }
  }

  /* ── Light mode (:global keeps the html-level [data-theme] unscoped) ── */
  :global([data-theme="light"]) #how .step h3 { color: var(--charcoal-900); }
  :global([data-theme="light"]) #how .step p { color: var(--charcoal-600); }
  :global([data-theme="light"]) #how .step-num { color: var(--amber-600); }
</style>
